<h1 style="font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 12px;">Still no data — escalating to you</h1>
<p>Hi <%= @tenant.gm_name %>,</p>
<p>
  We've been chasing
  <strong><%= @request.metric_key.to_s.tr("_", " ") %></strong>
  for <strong><%= @prompt.scheduled_for.in_time_zone(@tenant.time_zone).strftime("%B %Y") %></strong>
  and haven't gotten it yet — bringing this to your attention so it doesn't slip further.
</p>
<% chain = Array(@payload[:fallback_chain]).compact %>
<% if chain.any? %>
  <p>People we've already pinged:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><%= @source.configured_by_contact&.email || "(original contact)" %> (primary)</li>
    <% chain.each do |email| %>
      <li><%= email %> (fallback)</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>
<p>Want to take it on yourself, or pick someone new? Reply to your weekly digest or hit the link below.</p>
